- Build genai apps on AWS
- Fully managed
- Keep control of data used to train the model
- Pay-per-use pricing
- Unified APIs
- Leverage  wide array of foundational models
- RAG, LLM agents are out of box
- Security, Privacy and Responsible AI features
- It makes a copy of FM available only to you 
which you can finetune with your own data.


